  - Title: Tao Te Ching
    Chapter: XLI
Tags:
  - Life-Love=The Primordial State=Materia Prima and Human Perfection
Format: verse
---
When the inferior scholar is told of Tao.
He laughs aloud at it.
If it were not laughed at. it would not be sufficient to be Tao.
